Creates a visualization of a git repository's programming languages over time.

Usage
-----

Run stats calculations and image generation independently. Useful for working
on or debugging either part of the process.

    linecount.sh GIT_REPOSITORY OUT_PATH
        
        GIT_REPOSITORY may be any git path or URL
        OUT_PATH is the path to which output (e.g. images, CSV) will be placed.

    run_linevis.R OUT_PATH

        OUT_PATH is the path to which output (e.g. images, CSV) will be placed.

Run stats calculations and image generation together:

   run.sh GIT_REPOSITORY OUT_PATH 

        GIT_REPOSITORY may be any git path or URL
        OUT_PATH is the path to which output (e.g. images, CSV) will be placed.
